					<TD bgColor=white class=view>&nbsp; &nbsp; <font color=#010080><a href='mailto:navido@moneytoday.co.kr'>김준형</a> 기자 &nbsp; | &nbsp; 08/29 17:38 &nbsp; | &nbsp; 조회 6686 &nbsp; &nbsp;</font></TD></TR>
